{"tid":1778080,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"教師上水被捕　教育局要求考慮暫停職務","createTime":"2019-12-10T16:13:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T03:30:02.000Z","uid":291199,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b01b0f501158d76026fb81ea06653b8a2be206d2","tid":1778080,"uid":291199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:13:08.000Z","msg":"警方昨凌晨在上水天平邨拘捕12人，發現有人涉嫌管有鐵釘、電鑽、白電油等，被捕者包括1名教師。教育局今晚（10日）回覆查詢稱，已要求學校「應履行其作為僱主，以及確保學生安全的責任，考慮暫停該教師的職務」。另外，有30名教師在反修例運動中言行遭人投訴並且成立，有待懲處。 <br />\n<br />\n30教師遭投訴成立待懲處<br />\n<br />\n教育局指出，自6月中至11月初，已就106宗與近期社會事件有關的教師專業操守個案展開調查，初步完成60宗個案調查，包括早前已發出譴責信的兩宗個案；當中約30宗初步成立，正考慮作出懲處。至於被捕教師的數目，局方稱，由於涉及法律程序，現階段不便評論，如確立教師有違法行為，「他們除了要承擔法律責任外，教育局會根據《教育條例》嚴肅跟進，若情況嚴重，可以取消其教師註冊」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/498203090239831/posts/2725578110835640?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F498203090239831%2Fposts%2F2725578110835640%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwkXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=f1a949dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/498203090239831/posts/2725578110835640?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌未判先審<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0f3b9b49971ae621a9e5660228cf7da73e3454a","tid":1778080,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:30:21.000Z","msg":"[行動]和你踩！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778037\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778037</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a105e4f0ead9e20b3c5458c3ba4a3bcaea723089","tid":1778080,"uid":38793,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:31:54.000Z","msg":"無罪推定 哈"},{"pid":"e959d24497a8485f590ef40c2b9466883fec4ca0","tid":1778080,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2